                                "stop": 13.259,
                                "byte_start": 80004,
                                "byte_stop": 133085,
                                "text": "The judgments and opinion of the court in 76-695 Board of Curators of University of Missouri against Horowitz which will be announced by Mr. Justice Rehnquist."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 13.259,
                        "stop": 130.75,
                        "byte_start": 133085,
                        "byte_stop": 603080,
